Package: nanoporeQC
Type: Package
Title: Read Accuracy Analysis for Oxford Nanopore Sequencing Data
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Marko Suokas <your.email@example.com>
Maintainer: Marko Suokas <your.email@example.com>
Description: Provides a tool for analyzing Oxford Nanopore sequencing data quality.
    Tool takes advantage of known sequence of the DNA CS standard, aligns reads to
    the reference and calculates sequencing accuracy. The function creates a plot
    showing read accuracy distribution swith statistics.
